19 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 335 of Title 61, unless there is
21 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 A. Any person may forage for nuts and edible plants or fungi on
23 state-owned or state-managed property accessible to the public for
24
